    <lb n="34"/>εἴκοσι ὀκτώ <num value="28"/>, καὶ τῷ <num value="28">κη</num> <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτει</ex></expan> ὁμοίως <add place="supralinear">ἄλλ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ον</supplied></add> χιτῶ-

