    <lb n="40"/>των ἀργήσῃ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἢ ἀσ</supplied>θενήσῃ ἢ ἀτακτήσῃ ἢ 

    <lb n="41"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear>ι᾽ ἄλλην τι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὰ αἰ</supplied>τίαν ἡμέρας ἐπὶ τὰς 

